{"title":"Bjorn Riley Unveils Custom U.S. Champion Spark RC XC Bike with His Own Artistic Spin","link":"https://bikerumor.com/bjorn-riley-unveils-custom-u-s-champion-spark-rc/","date":1747897200000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-1536x1024.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN RILEY US CHAMP SPARK RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER\" /></p>\n<p>From podiums to paintbrushes, SCOTT-SRAM’s Bjorn Riley isn’t your average XC racer—and his new custom-painted U.S. XC Champion Edition Spark RC mountain bike proves it. Fresh off a breakout U23 season and a pair of Elite national titles. Riley is celebrating in full color, bringing his creative vision to the curvy canvas that is his race bike.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-name--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"2048\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-name--scaled.webp\" alt=\"SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN RILEY US CHAMP SPARK RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER name\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-name--scaled.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-name--240x300.webp 240w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-name--1536x1920.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-name--96x120.webp 96w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-name--768x960.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-name--1229x1536.webp 1229w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-name--1639x2048.webp 1639w\" /></a><figcaption><em>(All bike profile photos / Jacques Grobler)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Call it a rolling gallery of speed and self-expression. Designed and detailed by Riley himself, this special Spark RC World Cup is as personal as it gets. For the theme, Riley blends his performance pedigree with an athlete’s bold, tattooed visuals. One who lives just as much in the art studio as he does racing between the tape.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Scott Spark RC mountain bike of US XCO Champ Bjorn Riley</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-side--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"2048\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-side--scaled.webp\" alt=\"SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN RILEY US CHAMP SPARK RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-side--scaled.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-side--240x300.webp 240w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-side--1536x1920.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-side--96x120.webp 96w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-side--768x960.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-side--1229x1536.webp 1229w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-side--1638x2048.webp 1638w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>“This is my bike,”</em> Riley says.<em> “I mean it fully is my bike, it’s no one else’s. I’ve been dreaming of that moment since I was a little kid.”</em></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>From Boulder to the Big Leagues</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-Bjorn-jpg-e1747847287502.webp\"><img width=\"5983\" height=\"4727\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-Bjorn-jpg-e1747847287502.webp\" alt=\"SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN RILEY US CHAMP SPARK RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER Bjorn\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-Bjorn-jpg-e1747847287502.webp 5983w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-Bjorn-jpg-e1747847287502-297x235.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-Bjorn-jpg-e1747847287502-120x95.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-Bjorn-jpg-e1747847287502-768x607.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-Bjorn-jpg-e1747847287502-1536x1214.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-Bjorn-jpg-e1747847287502-2048x1618.webp 2048w\" /></a><figcaption><em>(Photo / Jacques Grobler)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Based in Salt Lake City but born from Boulder roots, Riley’s riding style already turned heads last season—two World Cup wins in Les Gets (XCC and XCO), and a string of U23 podiums capped by a <em>double</em> win at the U.S. Nationals in Macungie, PA, where he took home both the Elite XCO and XCC titles. Not bad for your first year mixing it up in the biggest bicycle big leagues.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-jumps--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-jumps--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Photo for Scott Sram MTB Team. Photo Sam Clark. clarkst@gmail.com\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-jumps--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-jumps--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-jumps--1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-jumps--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-jumps--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-jumps--2048x1365.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-jumps--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-jumps--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption><em>(Photo by Sam Clark / Scott-SRAM MTB Team)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But it’s not just his legs doing the talking—Riley’s got a distinctive flair that goes beyond race results. Whether it’s throwing style off tech features mid-race or blending bold visuals into his off-bike persona, he’s carving a unique line in the world of XC.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>U.S. Champion’s Custom Scott Spark RC with Artist’s Touch</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-SRAM--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-SRAM--scaled.webp\" alt=\"SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN RILEY US CHAMP SPARK RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER SRAM\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-SRAM--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-SRAM--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-SRAM--1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-SRAM--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-SRAM--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-SRAM--2048x1365.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-SRAM--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-SRAM--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Riley’s U.S. Champion edition Spark RC World Cup is more than just a one-off paint job. It reflects the athlete himself—raw, expressive, and full of contrast.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_B