back--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-back--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-back--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-back--2048x1365.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-back--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-back--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The graphics are a mash-up of Americana, traditional tattoo art, graffiti textures, and hidden personal symbols—like the subtle seattube detail that Riley says reminds him this isn’t just a machine, but a part of who he is.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-full--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-full--1536x1920.webp\" alt=\"SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN RILEY US CHAMP SPARK RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER full\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-full--1536x1920.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-full--240x300.webp 240w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-full--96x120.webp 96w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-full--768x960.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-full--1229x1536.webp 1229w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-full--1638x2048.webp 1638w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-full--scaled.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-flag--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-flag--1536x1024.webp\" alt=\"SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN RILEY US CHAMP SPARK RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER flag\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-flag--1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-flag--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-flag--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-flag--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-flag--2048x1365.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-flag--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-flag--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Scott’s <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2022-scott-spark-gets-bold-new-redesign-as-a-slack-fast-fully-integrated-120mm-xc-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">Spark RC platform</a> is already a race weapon, proven on the XC circuit for several years. It’s the bike of <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/pro-bike-check-nino-schurters-custom-scott-spark-rc/\">Muti-Time World Champion Nino Schurter </a>and the entire SCOTT SRAM squad. And really, it’s probably the single pro mountain bike <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=scott+spark+pro+bike\" target=\"_blank\">we’ve featured most</a> over the years, with all the wins racked up on this platform. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Riley’s version cranks that race-day energy up to eleven with his signature visual vibe and its one-of-a-kind graphics.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-rolling--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-rolling--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Photo for Scott Sram MTB Team. Photo Sam Clark. clarkst@gmail.com\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-rolling--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-rolling--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-rolling--1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-rolling--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-rolling--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-rolling--2048x1365.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-rolling--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SCOTT-SRAM_BJORN-RILEY-US-CHAMP-SPARK-RCPHOTO_BY_JACQUESGROBLER-rolling--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption><em>(Photo by Sam Clark / Scott-SRAM MTB Team)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Make sure to follow Riley and the UCI Mountain Bike World Series this coming weekend, May 23–25th in <a href=\"https://ucimtbworldseries.com/events\">Nové Město Na Moravě, Czechia for an XCO/ XCC showdown. </a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/bjorn-riley-unveils-custom-u-s-champion-spark-rc/\">Bjorn Riley Unveils Custom U.S. Champion Spark RC XC Bike with His Own Artistic Spin</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jordan Villella","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"4fe518a2c3e6ef3dd59d51eb4da422217d2c5fa449ec6a93643a558128634d15","category":"Cycling"}